        <div class="preview-phone">
          <div class="preview-screen">
            <div class="mini-notify">
              <div class="mini-title" id="previewTitle">愛車の相場が12万円UP</div>
              <div class="mini-body" id="previewBody">週2回まで、相場変動と売り時だけ通知します。</div>
